description: PIMS 3530 BD FSP Expanding and Diversifying the National System of Protected Areas in the Philippines

subproject.description: The project will achieve: (1) Protected Area system of the Philippines has been expanded under new and diverse management regimes ( ancestral domain, local government and community management areas) to cover an additional 400,000 hectares  of Key Biodiversity Area(KBAs) and with enhanced potential for further expansion;  (2) improved conservation effectiveness through enhanced systemic, institutional and individual capacities; (3) enhanced sustainability of the terrestrial PA system.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Expanding&Diversifying PA Proj

subproject.corporate outcome: Development plans and programmes integrate environmentally sustainable solutions in a manner that promotes poverty reduction, MDG achievement and low-emission climate-resilient development
